            <div class="steps-content">
                <div class="step-card" id="install-step1">
                    <div class="step-card-header">
                        <div class="step-number-large">01</div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="step-card-label">Step One</span>
                            <h3>Choose the Installation Location</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <p>Select a spot that gives RADCam a clear, unobstructed view of the area you want monitored. The location should be within reach of a power outlet, or plan to use a weatherproof extension cable.</p>
                        <div class="tip-box">
                            <div class="tip-box-icon">⚠️</div>
                            <p><strong>Avoid:</strong> Excessive direct sunlight, heavy rain exposure without overhang protection, or extreme shadows that may affect video quality and AI detection accuracy.</p>
